query: SELECT d.id, d.user_id, d.distributor_code, d.sponsor_id, d.rank, d.status, u.name, u.email FROM distributors d JOIN users u ON d.user_id = u.id WHERE u.name LIKE '%Dakota%' OR d.distributor_code = 'NEON1VDTXNY' LIMIT 5;
